Firebase Hosting {
  inside console.

  npm i -g firebase-tools
  npm run build
  firebase login:ci -> login in firebase 
  firebase init -> initialise firebase 
  Yes-> Enter->use build-> Yes for single page / Dont make automatic builds 
  firebase deploy -> deploy 
}

